Adds_Clockwork Onmyoji_Status_Mini_Desc: Shrunk to a fraction of your normal size. Damage dealt and movement speed are reduced, while damage taken is increased.
ContentDesc_Die Mechanische Menagerie:
A dazzling array of arenas await at the Grand Companies' glamour-woven tactical training grounds. Designed with adventurers in mind, these strategic confrontations of but few competitors make for a thrilling challenge for newcome pups and Wolves' Den regulars alike.



At the end of the crystal line, who will stand victorious? Will it be you?



※Match results will affect Rising Stars and Crystal Credit.

※Players with comparable PvP tiers and risers will be matched with one another.

※Parties will be sorted by role, tier, riser, and credit to ensure relatively equal averages.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36100_Text: Welcome one, welcome all, to Kageyama's Clockwork Castletown! Gahahaha!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36101_Text: Fires and fights are the flowers of Kugane! Now, entertain me, peasants!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36102_Text: Hm, needs more sound and fury... Let the parade commence!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36103_Text: Dance, my puppets, dance! But have care where you wander...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36104_Text: Now, you can't expect clockwork to do all the work for you.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_36105_Text: Oh, I seem to have dropped a coin. And another. And another!
